### LabVerse Android App - User API Test Suite
### Base URL: http://10.0.2.2:8081/api/users/
### Note: 10.0.2.2 is the Android emulator's alias for localhost

@baseUrl = http://10.0.2.2:8081/api/users
@contentType = application/json

### Variables
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@userId = YOUR_USER_ID_HERE
@email = test@example.com

### 1. Get Current User
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 2. Get User by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{userId}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 3. Get User by Email
GET {{baseUrl}}/email/{{email}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 4. Update Profile
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "updateduser",
  "fullName": "Updated Name",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/avatar.png"
}

### 5. Change Password
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/me/password
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "oldPassword": "password123",
  "newPassword": "newpassword123"
}

